msgstr "Unir atributos por proximidad"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1923
msgid ""
"Takes an input vector layer and creates a new vector layer with additional "
"fields in its attribute table. The additional attributes and their values "
"are taken from a second vector layer. Features are joined by finding the "
"closest features from each layer."
msgstr ""
"Toma una capa de vector de entrada y crea una nueva capa de vector con "
"campos adicionales en su tabla de atributos. Los atributos adicionales y sus"
" valores se toman de una segunda capa vectorial. Las entidades se unen "
"buscando las entidades más cercanas de cada capa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1929
msgid ""
"By default only the nearest feature is joined, but the join can also join to"
" the k-nearest neighboring features."
msgstr ""
"De forma predeterminada, solo se une la entidad más cercana, pero la unión "
"también puede unirse a las k entidades vecinas más cercanas."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1932
msgid ""
"If a maximum distance is specified, only features which are closer than this"
" distance will be matched."
msgstr ""
"Si se especifica una distancia máxima, solo se igualarán las entidades que "
"estén más cerca que esta distancia."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1938
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisnearestneighbouranalysis`, :ref:`qgisjoinattributestable`, "
":ref:`qgisjoinattributesbylocation`, :ref:`qgisdistancematrix`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisnearestneighbouranalysis`, :ref:`qgisjoinattributestable`, "
":ref:`qgisjoinattributesbylocation`, :ref:`qgisdistancematrix`"

