msgstr "La capa vectorial saliente."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2660
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:splitfeaturesbycharacter``"
msgstr "**ID Algoritmo**: ``native:splitfeaturesbycharacter``"

